00:38:47,120 --> 00:38:50,720
They'd make like three adult comedies a year and they had a lot of good ones.

358
00:38:52,820 --> 00:38:58,160
None of them are available to be found on Blu -ray for whatever reason, so there's got to be some sort of rights thing.

359
00:38:58,600 --> 00:39:07,080
It's like they did Outrageous Fortune with Shelly Long, Big Business, Stakeout. They did all kinds of movies, Touchstone.

